headline: 5 Non-Tech Nasdaq Composite High Flyers to Buy for More Gains Ahead
summary: These five stocks have provided 50% returns year to date. Despite the rally, their favorable Zacks Rank indicates more room to run. The stocks are: AXON, UAL, ISRG, SFM, FOX.

headline: BlackRock Mid-Cap Growth Equity Fund Q3 2024 Commentary
